<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your 9ja Market Marketer Application</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .container {
        border: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #009933;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
        font-size: 0.8em;
        color: #888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>9ja Market</h1>
        <p>Your Application is Being Reviewed</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</p>

        <p>
          Thank you for applying to become a Marketer with 9ja Market! We're
          excited about your interest in partnering with us to help local
          merchants thrive in the digital marketplace.
        </p>

        <p>
          Your application with username <strong><%= username %></strong> has
          been received and is currently under review by our team. This process
          typically takes 1-3 business days.
        </p>

        <h3>What happens next?</h3>
        <p>
          Once your information and credentials have been verified, we'll send
          you another email with your unique referrer code and comprehensive
          instructions on how to start earning commissions by onboarding
          merchants to our platform.
        </p>

        <p>
          In the meantime, you can learn more about our platform and the
          benefits we offer to merchants by visiting our website.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our
          support team.
        </p>

        <p>
          Thank you for your patience and for choosing to partner with 9ja
          Market!
        </p>

        <p>
          Best regards,<br />
          The 9ja Market Team
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> 9ja Market. All rights
          reserved.
        </p>
        <p>
          This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this
          email.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
